  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended for predicting absolute hemolysis indices at operating points representative of Class III VAD implant use. Model Risk Level 5 applies; all 13 credibility factors have been assessed against MRL-5 thresholds. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; detailed Context of Use scope is documented in the bound Claim and Requirement records.",
