      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests against manufactured solutions required for all governing equation sets at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy verification performed for momentum equations; scalar transport (hemolysis damage integral) lacks manufactured-solution verification, yielding achieved level 3."
    },
