      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation with GCI reporting on hemolysis index QoI required; three systematically refined meshes mandatory.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study completed for velocity field; hemolysis index GCI computed but asymptotic range not fully achieved, limiting achieved level to 3."
    },
    {
