      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must match VAD operating envelope within stated tolerances; inlet flow waveform fidelity documented.",
      "rationale": "Steady-state bench conditions match nominal VAD operating point; pulsatile inlet waveform representative of in-vivo VAD use not replicated in validation experiments."
