      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E% or validation uncertainty) reported for hemolysis index and velocity field; uncertainty bands must overlap at 95% confidence.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions exceed experimental values by 18–34% across operating points; validation uncertainty bands do not consistently overlap, achieved level 2."
