      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (hemolysis index, shear stress distribution) must directly map to device safety endpoints specified in the regulatory submission.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is a direct regulatory QoI; sub-lethal platelet activation index identified as additional relevant QoI but not computed, limiting achieved level to 3."
